    <div class="container">
                    <div class="footer block block-serapid-footer-block-en block-odd first">
    <div class="footer-techno">
        <div class="footer-techno-text"><span class="title">Rigid Chain Technology</span>SERAPID has been working in the field of linear movement equipment for 45 years. SERAPID elevation and transfer systems are designed using a simple mechanical principle making it possible to transfer loads of a few kilograms to several hundred tonnes. This is accomplished using Rigid Chain Technology (RCT).<br />
<br />
This technology is based on interlocking links. When the chain is deployed it behaves as a true rigid pushing bar. When retracted, the chain unlocks in the drive casing and stores in a reduced space.</div>
        <div class="footer-techno-link"><a href="/en/rigid-chain-technology">Read more</a></div>
